<frame cBy="JKR" cDate="04/11/2005 09:26:14 PDT Mon" name="Desirable_event" ID="1383" xsi:schemaLocation="../schema/frame.xsd" xmlns="http://framenet.icsi.berkeley.edu" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
    <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;A particular &lt;fen&gt;State_of_affairs&lt;/fen&gt; is desirable.  The &lt;fen&gt;State_of_affairs&lt;/fen&gt; may be required to achieve a &lt;fen&gt;Purpose&lt;/fen&gt;.  A set of &lt;fen&gt;Circumstances&lt;/fen&gt; may be specified under which the assessment of desirability holds.


&lt;ex&gt;&lt;fex name="sta"&gt;You&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;should&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="sta"&gt;take the doses about 12 hours apart and at the same time each day&lt;/fex&gt;.&lt;/ex&gt;
&lt;ex&gt; &lt;fex name="cir"&gt;If the metal is seriously rusted or warped&lt;/fex&gt;, &lt;fex name="sta"&gt;it&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;should&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="sta"&gt;be repaired or replaced with a chimney top damper&lt;/fex&gt;.&lt;/ex&gt;
&lt;ex&gt;&lt;fex name="pur"&gt;To ensure that&lt;/fex&gt;, &lt;fex name="sta"&gt;you&lt;/fex&gt; &lt;t&gt;should&lt;/t&gt; &lt;fex name="sta"&gt;have no CLASSPATH set&lt;/fex&gt;.&lt;/ex&gt;&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
    <FE bgColor="FF0000" fgColor="FFFFFF" coreType="Core" cBy="JKR" cDate="04/11/2005 09:28:39 PDT Mon" abbrev="sta" name="State_of_affairs" ID="7756">
        <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;The &lt;fen&gt;State_of_affairs&lt;/fen&gt; that the speaker finds desirable.&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
    </FE>
    <FE bgColor="800080" fgColor="FFFFFF" coreType="Extra-Thematic" cBy="JKR" cDate="04/11/2005 09:29:59 PDT Mon" abbrev="cir" name="Circumstances" ID="7757">
        <definition>&lt;def-root&gt;The FE &lt;fen&gt;Circumstances&lt;/fen&gt; encodes a setting, often temporal or spatial, within which the &lt;fen&gt;State_of_affairs&lt;/fen&gt; has the specified assessment of desirability.&lt;/def-root&gt;</definition>
    </FE>
    <FE bgColor="0000FF" fgColor="FFFFFF" coreType="Peripheral" cBy="JKR" cDate="04/11/2005 09:31:25 PDT Mon" abbrev="pur" name="Purpose" ID="7758">
